text: Neumarkt () is a Landkreis (district) in Bavaria, Germany. ==Geography== The district is in the mountains of the Franconian Jura. The southern parts are occupied by the Altmühl Valley Nature Park. ==Towns and municipalities== Towns Municipalities #Berching #Dietfurt #Freystadt #Neumarkt #Parsberg #Velburg #Berg #Berngau #Breitenbrunn #Deining #Hohenfels #Lauterhofen 7.
